This dataset contains structural (T1w) and functional MRI data from participants performing three tasks:
- Response task
- Feature task
- Dimension task

Acquisition parameters:
- Scanner: Siemens Magnetom Prisma 3T
- Functional TR: 2.0s, voxel size: 3mm isotropic
- T1w: 1mm isotropic

Participants:
- Healthy young adults (N = 53)

Notes:
- Localizer scans were excluded from the BIDS dataset.
- Functional runs include AP and PA phase-encoding directions.
